---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="公积金法拍房 - 广西房产金融服务">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent text-white py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">公积金法拍房</h1>
      <p class="text-xl">低于市场价30% | 专业全程代办 | 风险全程把控</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">为什么选择法拍房？</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl text-accent mb-4">💰</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">价格优势</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">低于市场价20%-40%</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl text-accent mb-4">📈</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">升值空间</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">长期持有潜力大</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl text-accent mb-4">🏠</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">租金收益</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">可出租获取现金流</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">我们的服务</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-12">
        <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-accent mr-2">✓</span> 房源筛选：专业平台筛选优质房源</li>
        <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-accent mr-2">✓</span> 尽职调查：产权、税费、现状全面调查</li>
        <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-accent mr-2">✓</span> 竞拍支持：专业竞拍策略指导</li>
        <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-accent mr-2">✓</span> 过户代办：法院裁定、产权过户全程代办</li>
        <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-accent mr-2">✓</span> 风险控制：法律保障，资金安全</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">风险提示</h2>
      <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-4 mb-12">
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>⚠️ 清场风险：原业主不配合搬离</li>
          <li>⚠️ 税费风险：欠缴税费需买受人承担</li>
          <li>⚠️ 产权风险：产权不清晰或有纠纷</li>
          <li>⚠️ 贷款风险：部分银行不支持法拍房贷款</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">办理流程</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 mb-12">
        <div class="step-card">① 房源筛选</div>
        <div class="step-card">② 尽职调查</div>
        <div class="step-card">③ 资金准备</div>
        <div class="step-card">④ 报名竞拍</div>
        <div class="step-card">⑤ 成功竞拍</div>
        <div class="step-card">⑥ 过户入住</div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-xl text-center">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">立即预约免费咨询</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">专业团队为您保驾护航</p>
        <a href="tel:17200861361" class="btn-primary text-lg px-10">📞 172-0086-1361</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .step-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>